    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460313_36_609-624",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "609-624",
      "markText": "天下事不难办，总是得人为难尔。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460313&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=609&rangeEnd=624",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a332ce0724adb990a3c8f8?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=609&rangeEnd=624"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460313_75_3973-4032",
      "chapterUid": 75,
      "range": "3973-4032",
      "markText": "小时拘束太严，大来纵肆⑤，反多不可收拾⑥；或渐近憨呆，不晓世事，皆必有之患",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460313&chapterUid=75&rangeStart=3973&rangeEnd=4032",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a332ce0724adb990a3c8f8?chapterUid=75&rangeStart=3973&rangeEnd=4032"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460313_10_7433-7488",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "7433-7488",
      "markText": "用财有道，自奉宁过于俭，待人宁过于厚，寻常酬应则酌于施报可也。济人之道，先其亲者，后其疏者；先其急者，次其缓者",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460313&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=7433&rangeEnd=7488",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a332ce0724adb990a3c8f8?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=7433&rangeEnd=7488"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460313_12_9157-9236",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "9157-9236",
      "markText": "同学之友，如果诚实发愤，无妄言妄动，固宜引为同类。倘或不然，则同斋①割席②，勿与亲昵③为要。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460313&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=9157&rangeEnd=9236",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a332ce0724adb990a3c8f8?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=9157&rangeEnd=9236"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460313_53_456-485",
      "chapterUid": 53,
      "range": "456-485",
      "markText": "尔年轻学浅，无阅历，凡事以少开口、莫高兴为主，记之，记之。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460313&chapterUid=53&rangeStart=456&rangeEnd=485",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a332ce0724adb990a3c8f8?chapterUid=53&rangeStart=456&rangeEnd=485"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460313_78_757-793",
      "chapterUid": 78,
      "range": "757-793",
      "markText": "诸孙之贤不肖，则尔兄弟夫妇之贤不肖⑤也，尚慎之哉！",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460313&chapterUid=78&rangeStart=757&rangeEnd=793",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a332ce0724adb990a3c8f8?chapterUid=78&rangeStart=757&rangeEnd=793"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460313_3_5029-5061",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "5029-5061",
      "markText": "读书不必急求进功，只要有恒无间，养得此心纯一专静，自然所学日进耳",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460313&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5029&rangeEnd=5061",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a332ce0724adb990a3c8f8?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5029&rangeEnd=5061"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460313_30_494-589",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "494-589",
      "markText": "尔年十六七，正是读书时候，能苦心力学，作一明白秀才，无坠门风②，即是幸事。如其不然③，即少年登科④，有何好处？且正古人所忧也",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460313&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=494&rangeEnd=589",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a332ce0724adb990a3c8f8?chapterUid=30&rangeStart=494&rangeEnd=589"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460313_72_710-770",
      "chapterUid": 72,
      "range": "710-770",
      "markText": "吾总以世泽之兴隆要多出勤耕苦读子弟，家祚③之昌盛总在忠孝节义④，他不足贵也。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460313&chapterUid=72&rangeStart=710&rangeEnd=770",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a332ce0724adb990a3c8f8?chapterUid=72&rangeStart=710&rangeEnd=770"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460313_3_6829-6910",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "6829-6910",
      "markText": "不求早达，只愿厚积薄发。他告诫孝威：“自古功名振世之人，大都早年备尝辛苦，至晚岁事权到手乃有建树，未闻早达而能大有所成者。天道非翕聚不能发舒，人事非历练不能通晓。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460313&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6829&rangeEnd=6910",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a332ce0724adb990a3c8f8?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6829&rangeEnd=6910"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460313_3_7611-7650",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "7611-7650",
      "markText": "以有恒治学，不要一曝十寒，根据各自身体和心性因材施教，这是符合儿童教育规律的。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460313&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7611&rangeEnd=7650",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a332ce0724adb990a3c8f8?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7611&rangeEnd=7650"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460313_3_7401-7472",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "7401-7472",
      "markText": "以体质非佳，苦读能伤气，久坐能伤血。小时拘束太严，大来纵肆，反多不可收拾；或渐近憨呆，不晓世事，皆必有之患”。只要有恒，不必追促，以养身为要。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460313&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7401&rangeEnd=7472",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a332ce0724adb990a3c8f8?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7401&rangeEnd=7472"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460313_7_643-732",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "643-732",
      "markText": "吾所以教之者，先以义理⑪正其心，继以经济⑫廓其志⑬，至文章之工拙⑭、科名之得失，非所急也。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460313&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=643&rangeEnd=732",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a332ce0724adb990a3c8f8?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=643&rangeEnd=732"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460313_12_2913-3030",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "2913-3030",
      "markText": "志患不立，尤患不坚。偶然听一段好话，听一件好事，亦知歆动④羡慕，当时亦说我要与他一样。不过几日几时，此念就不知如何销歇⑤去了，此是尔志不坚，还由不能立志之故。如果一心向上，有何事业不能做成？",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460313&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=2913&rangeEnd=3030",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a332ce0724adb990a3c8f8?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=2913&rangeEnd=3030"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460313_21_748-793",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "748-793",
      "markText": "吾湘在东南最为福地，尔辈未经兵燹之酷，直不知人世间危险困苦有非言语所能尽者，故略为尔道之。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460313&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=748&rangeEnd=793",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a332ce0724adb990a3c8f8?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=748&rangeEnd=793"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460313_34_692-802",
      "chapterUid": 34,
      "range": "692-802",
      "markText": "间有一二曾由八股得科名者，其心思较之他人尚易入理，与之说几句《四书》，说几句《大注》④，即目前事物随时指点，是较未读书之人容易开悟许多。可见真作八股者必体玩书理，时有几句圣贤话头留在口边究是不同也。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460313&chapterUid=34&rangeStart=692&rangeEnd=802",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a332ce0724adb990a3c8f8?chapterUid=34&rangeStart=692&rangeEnd=802"
